geomerative
Class RMesh

java.lang.Object
  geomerative.RGeomElem
      geomerative.RMesh

public class RMesh
extends RGeomElem

RMesh is a reduced interface for creating, holding and drawing meshes. Meshes are a group of tiangle strips (RStrip).
